{"data":[{"date":"10:12 10/07","title":"Ashley Young c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/su-tro-lai-ruc-ro-cua-binh-doan-quy-do.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ashley Young ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam s\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ea3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ashley Young khuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u1eef \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111i nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u1ede b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh S\u01b0 t\u1eed Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ashley Young ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ashley Young ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/su-tro-lai-ruc-ro-cua-binh-doan-quy-do.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ashley Young n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 ho\u1eb7c Ph\u00e1p. Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m th\u00ec Tam s\u01b0 m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Ashley Young ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam s\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ea3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec trong tay c\u1ea3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. V\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadp trung \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p th\u00edch h\u1ee3p. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ashley Young tin Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n Croatia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i nh\u00e0n nh\u00e3 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Croatia ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 11m m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Croatia vs Anh\" title=\"Preview Croatia vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Anh-vs-Croatia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Young tin Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n Croatia v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Ashley Young\u00a0th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n Croatia v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t Anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, Croatia ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 120 ph\u00fat trong c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 11m m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Croatia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u00e0o m\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/eric-dier-chi-ra-2-cau-thu-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-croatia-421-190830.html\" target=\"_blank\">Eric Dier c\u0169ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Spurs khuy\u00ean Tam s\u01b0 c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Rakitic v\u00e0 Modric c\u1ee7a Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1104","checkdouble":"190832"},{"date":"10:58 10/07","title":"Lovren \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1o th\u00f9 Harry Kane","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/lov.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, trung v\u1ec7 Dejan Lovren th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Harry Kane v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\r\n</h2><h2>Lovren s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y &ndash; Harry Kane. B\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc ca-ro c\u1ea7n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Croatia, v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Dejan Lovren n\u1eafm tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u00c1 qu\u00e2n Champions League, nh\u01b0ng Lovren t\u1eebng b\u1ecb Harry Kane s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, khi Liverpool thua th\u1ea3m Tottenham 1-4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lovren th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Harry Kane\" title=\"Lovren th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Harry Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/lov.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Harry Kane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 The Kop cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Kane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi ca t\u1ee5ng. Trong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Kane lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ghi tr\u00ean 25 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a, khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o hay b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. \u0110T Anh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Croatia mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, gi\u1ed1ng Argentina, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3&rdquo; &ndash; Lovren th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Harry Kane v\u00e0 Tam S\u01b0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quay ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 9 th\u00e1ng, Dejan Lovren khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Harry Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tottenham qua m\u1eb7t, m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. Ch\u1ec9 30 ph\u00fat sau khi b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, anh b\u1ecb HLV Jurgen Klopp r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Lovren, v\u00e0 anh \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-croatia-mat-hlv-vi-khieu-khich-chu-nha-nga-421-190822.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/dt-croatia-mat-hlv-vi-khieu-khich-chu-nha-nga.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-croatia-mat-hlv-vi-khieu-khich-chu-nha-nga-421-190822.html\">\u0110T Croatia m\u1ea5t HLV v\u00ec khi\u00eau kh\u00edch ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ee3 l\u00fd \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 \u00f4ng Ognjen Vukojevic m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eeba b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 do ch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\">HLV Croatia \u0111\u1ec1 cao Sterling tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh, HLV Croatia, Zlatko Dalic \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tam...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1103","checkdouble":"190834"},{"date":"10:54 10/07","title":"Buffon: \"Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Neymar m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/buffon-that-bai-tai-world-cup-2018-se-giup-neymar-manh-me-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 \u00e1o trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Anh r\u1ea5t th\u00edch s\u1ed1 1 nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Petr Cech.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bernd Leno ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayer Leverkusen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Arsenal x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Petr Cech, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi C\u1ed9ng H\u00f2a S\u00e9c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ecf \u00e1o s\u1ed1 33 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2018/19.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 \u00e1o nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i khi anh ra m\u1eaft Bayer Leverkusen, 19 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00c1o s\u1ed1 19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Santi Cazorla, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBernd Leno v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf Arsenal, nh\u01b0ng anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi Petr Cech r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi S\u00e9c c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Petr Cech</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190220.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua Leno</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Petr Cech m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, song nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho c\u1ef1u sao Bayer Leverkusen \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernd Leno\" title=\"Bernd Leno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/arsenal-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Petr Cech</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Leno \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Petr Cech qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7. HLV Unai Emery c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Leno b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f2n Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00fap. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c David Ospina s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, b\u1edfi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 3 c\u1ee7a Arsenal m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1102","checkdouble":"190835"},{"date":"11:09 10/07","title":"Buffon n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Juve chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/buffon-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-juve-chieu-mo-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a CLB PSG \u2013 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Gianluigi Buffon chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.\r\n</h2><h2>Buffon hy v\u1ecdng Ronaldo s\u1edbm sang Juve<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Cris Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Real Madrid, v\u00e0 \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh ra \u0111i. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin Juventus \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin t\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb&hellip; Buffon. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 40 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay CLB t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m c\u00f9ng CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p PSG. Ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng mong Juve s\u1edbm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3, \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t danh hi\u1ec7u C1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buffon chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo\" title=\"Buffon v\u00e0 Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/buffon-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-juve-chieu-mo-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Buffon chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus&rdquo; &ndash; Buffon cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Juve c\u1ea7n, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi cho m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra sau khi t\u00f4i ra \u0111i \u01b0, th\u00fa th\u1ef1c t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Ronaldo ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng Ronaldo s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Serie A. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Juve v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1&rdquo; &ndash; Buffon chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t, Buffon s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ronaldo, n\u1ebfu PSG ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Juve \u1edf Champions League. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Buffon s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Juve c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/5-thuong-vu-bom-tan-co-the-xay-ra-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-187-190765.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/5-thuong-vu-bom-tan-co-the-xay-ra-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/5-thuong-vu-bom-tan-co-the-xay-ra-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-187-190765.html\">5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cho m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u00e2y chuy\u1ec1n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/evra-khuyen-ronaldo-tu-choi-mu-gia-nhap-juventus-184-190744.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/evra-khuyen-ronaldo-tu-choi-mu-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/evra-khuyen-ronaldo-tu-choi-mu-gia-nhap-juventus-184-190744.html\">Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span><br>\r\nPatrice Evra tin r\u1eb1ng Juventus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1101","checkdouble":"190836"},{"date":"11:35 10/07","title":"\u0110\u1ebfn Wenger c\u0169ng s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Ozil phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/den-wenger-cung-soc-voi-ozil-phien-ban-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ngay c\u1ea3 Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 th\u1eddi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a anh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m n\u00ean th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c khi v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Joachim Loew s\u1edbm k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf World Cup 2018 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 80 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Wenger ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ozil sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Wenger ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ozil sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/den-wenger-cung-soc-voi-ozil-phien-ban-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Wenger ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ozil m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 hi\u1ec3u cho nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng phanh \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mesut Ozil. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3i g\u1ecdn chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n s\u00e2n c\u1ecf v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n d\u00ednh l\u00edu nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00ean l\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3, nh\u01b0 c\u00e3i nhau tay \u0111\u00f4i v\u1edbi C\u0110V hay ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh chung v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Arsene Wenger c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u01b0ng chi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal. Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i \u0111au l\u00f2ng ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch Ozil phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n World Cup 2018: \u201cTheo d\u00f5i Mesut thi \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng khi n\u00ean d\u00e2ng cao ch\u01a1i tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i y\u00ean v\u1ecb m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u to\u00e0n th\u00e1i qu\u00e1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u00f4i n\u00e0o, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Ozil m\u00e0 t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft, l\u00e0 Ozil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 Ozil m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat thanh tho\u00e1t, t\u1ef1 do n\u00e0o h\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ki\u1ec1m h\u00e3m l\u1ea1i m\u1ed7i khi c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cD\u00f9 g\u00ec th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft, Ozil v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Gundogan \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup. B\u1ecdn h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb ph\u1ec9 b\u00e1ng \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c trong khi c\u00e1i c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 th\u00ec l\u1ea1i ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2u, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cho c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 sa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-duc-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-dau-roi-tinh-than-duc-466-189832.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/dt-duc-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-dau-roi-tinh-than-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-duc-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-dau-roi-tinh-than-duc-466-189832.html\">Mannschaft b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i tinh th\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ee9c?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i tinh th\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ee9c? Mannschaft r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 trong s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu nh\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 Mesut Ozil th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh cho m\u1ed9t Mannschaft thi\u1ebfu b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1100","checkdouble":"190839"},{"date":"11:16 10/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Bernd Leno ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 \u00e1o trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Anh r\u1ea5t th\u00edch s\u1ed1 1 nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Petr Cech.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bernd Leno ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayer Leverkusen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Arsenal x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Petr Cech, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi C\u1ed9ng H\u00f2a S\u00e9c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ecf \u00e1o s\u1ed1 33 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2018/19.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 \u00e1o nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i khi anh ra m\u1eaft Bayer Leverkusen, 19 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00c1o s\u1ed1 19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Santi Cazorla, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBernd Leno v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf Arsenal, nh\u01b0ng anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi Petr Cech r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi S\u00e9c c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Petr Cech</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190220.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua Leno</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Petr Cech m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, song nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho c\u1ef1u sao Bayer Leverkusen \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernd Leno\" title=\"Bernd Leno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/arsenal-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Petr Cech</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Leno \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Petr Cech qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7. HLV Unai Emery c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Leno b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f2n Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00fap. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c David Ospina s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, b\u1edfi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 3 c\u1ee7a Arsenal m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1099","checkdouble":"190840"},{"date":"11:02 10/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 10/7: MU ch\u1ed1t mua \"hung th\u1ea7n\" h\u1ea1 tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/ngay-hom-nay-107.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (10/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>MU ch\u1ed1t mua \"hung th\u1ea7n\" h\u1ea1 tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">MU \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao World Cup 2018 Hirving Lozano \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Mexico \u1edf ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh v\u00e0 t\u1eebng ghi b\u00e0n h\u1ea1 \"c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng\" \u0110\u1ee9c. T\u1edd Mexican newspaper Record ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, MU \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ebfn PSV.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 107, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 107, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Tin-nong-World-Cup-2018-ngay-186-Anh-manh,-nhung-van-kem-Bi-hinh-anh-4.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lozano</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Barca c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Arthur Melo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng Ba, Barcelona \u0111\u1ea1t tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn mua Arthur Melo t\u1eeb Gremio. H\u00f4m qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Arthur k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Barca, ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u euro (31 tri\u1ec7u euro tr\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 9 tri\u1ec7u euro ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed). Barca c\u0169ng c\u00e0i v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arthur \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 400 tri\u1ec7u euro. Arthur s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a Barca.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 107 MU ch\u1ed1t mua hung th\u1ea7n h\u1ea1 tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 107 MU ch\u1ed1t mua hung th\u1ea7n h\u1ea1 tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-107-MU-chot-mua-hung-than-ha-tuyen-Duc-hinh-anh-2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Melo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Kante l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trang tin th\u00e2n c\u1eadn v\u1edbi PSG, Paris United cho bi\u1ebft N\u2019Golo Kante l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Parc des Princes. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u00e0o di\u1ec5n ra do Chelsea kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1eadu h\u0129nh kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a PSG.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea-172-189414.html\">Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u1ea4n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Bild cho bi\u1ebft Robert Lewandowski \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf tham v\u1ecdng ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cb\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng\u201d \u1edf Anh ho\u1eb7c TBN. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern Munich sau khi \u201cr\u1edbt gi\u00e1\u201d th\u00ea th\u1ea3m b\u1edfi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec3n m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u00e0nh gi\u00e0nh Champions League v\u1edbi H\u00f9m x\u00e1m.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd cho sao tr\u1ebb \u1edf l\u1ea1i Newcastle</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Kenedy th\u00eam 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Bayern Munich hay PSG.</div>\r\n<h2>Barcelona mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 Nou Camp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Julian Draxler \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Barcelona. Trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thay th\u1ebf c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Iniesta, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Rakitic, Barca \u0111ang thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u1ede World Cup 2018, Draxler thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u00f2n \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1098","checkdouble":"190841"},{"date":"11:06 10/07","title":"3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/3-ly-do-de-tin-bi-se-danh-bai-phap-o-ban-ket-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Martinez ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n EURO 2016 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h00 s\u00e1ng mai 11/7 gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng gi\u1eefa hai \u0110T <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 </span>trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 Saint Petersburg.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n EURO c\u1ee7a hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0110T B\u1ec9. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin &lsquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf B\u1ec9&rsquo; s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean cu\u1ed9c l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Les Bleus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>B\u1ed9 n\u00e3o Martinez v\u00e0 &lsquo;ph\u00f3 t\u01b0\u1edbng&rsquo; Thierry Henry<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o t\u00e0i c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c HLV. V\u00e0 \u1edf kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 HLV Martinez v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 \u0111ang nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Didier Deschamps v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 s\u1eadu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y HLV Martinez \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho danh hi\u1ec7u HLV c\u1ee7a n\u0103m. D\u00f9 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i khi g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Nainggolan do kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang ch\u1ee9ng minh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/3-ly-do-de-tin-Bi-se-danh-bai-Phap-o-tran-Phap-vs-Bi-sap-toi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00fap \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu khi v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua t\u1ea1i AS Roma. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, &lsquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&rsquo; c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi to\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng cho t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi B\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out, HLV Martinez \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o Chadli v\u00e0 Fellaini, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Brazil h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh, \u00f4ng Martinez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00fap \u0110T B\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u0103ng hoa b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 5-3-2 \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 k\u1ec1m t\u1ecfa th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Neymar - Willian v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Martinez kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a Thierry Henry, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Am hi\u1ec3u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi HLV Deschamps, Henry ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean b\u1ed5 \u00edch cho BHL \u0110T B\u1ec9 trong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Henry s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edch cho B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>'Ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5' Eden Hazard <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, Eden Hazard \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Mang t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n, Hazard \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft &lsquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa qu\u1ef7&rsquo; t\u1ef1 tin th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n song c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Hazard l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil 2010, James Rodriguez 2014, va gio la Eden Hazard 20181\" title=\"Mesut Ozil 2010, James Rodriguez 2014, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Eden Hazard 20181\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/mesut-ozil-2010-james-rodriguez-2014-va-gio-la-eden-hazard-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;<em>Eden Hazard v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i Wolrd Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00f4ng minh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y trong vi\u1ec7c h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c &lsquo;v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba&rsquo;. V\u00e0 NHM \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng Hazard s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Hazard, trong tay HLV Martinez c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 De Bruyne, Lukaku, &hellip; \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Mbappe<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh \u0110T B\u1ec9, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">VCK World Cup 2018</span>&nbsp;khi b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ea1 th\u00eam Argentina v\u00e0 Uruguay tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Mbappe th\u00ec nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Les Bleus v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Griezmann c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11m, b\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i do sai l\u1ea7m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Oliver Giroud th\u00ec v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ghi b\u00e0n, t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 Ousmane Dembele, Nabil Fekir. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Pogba kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t \u1edf kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe roi san nhuong vi tri cho Dembele\" title=\"Mbappe r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Dembele\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/vermaelen-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-bi-vs-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Li\u1ec7u Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u1ebfu Mbappe b\u1ecb k\u00e8m ch\u1eb7t?&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Mbappe \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sau hai th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 n\u1ebfu s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd b\u1ecb phong t\u1ecfa?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Martinez s\u1ebd y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 k\u1eb9p ch\u1eb7t Mbappe. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Jan Vertonghen, Toby Alderweireld, Vincent Kompany,&nbsp;\u0110T B\u1ec9 d\u01b0 s\u1ee9c l\u00e0m chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2n hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 11/7): \u0110\u1ec9nh cao h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u1edf St. Petersburg</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o 90 ph\u00fat ho\u1eb7c d\u00e0i h\u01a1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/deschamps-cung-nhu-messi-hazard-se-tit-ngoi-truoc-kante-469-190828.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/deschamps-cung-nhu-messi-hazard-se-tit-ngoi-truoc-kante.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/deschamps-cung-nhu-messi-hazard-se-tit-ngoi-truoc-kante-469-190828.html\">Deschamps: Kante s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00e2m l\u1eb7ng</span><br>\r\nHLV Deschamps kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh N&rsquo;golo Kante s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 c\u00e2m l\u1eb7ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch anh l\u00e0m Messi t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 n\u0103m nay.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-co-nguy-co-bo-lo-tran-dau-phap-vs-bi-421-190807.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/mbappe-co-nguy-co-bo-lo-tran-dau-phap-vs-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-co-nguy-co-bo-lo-tran-dau-phap-vs-bi-421-190807.html\">R\u1ed9 tin Mbappe b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span><br>\r\nKylian Mbappe c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 khi v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Didier Deschamps l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c tr\u1ea5n an ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng c\u00e2u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi-465-190803.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi-465-190803.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span><br>\r\nHLV Roberto Martinez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p khi ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/quan-diem-bi-va-martinez-la-nhung-ong-but-cua-bong-da-421-190762.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/quan-diem-bi-va-martinez-la-nhung-ong-but-cua-bong-da.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/quan-diem-bi-va-martinez-la-nhung-ong-but-cua-bong-da-421-190762.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Martinez l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng &ldquo;\u00f4ng b\u1ee5t&rdquo; c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><br>\r\nRoberto Martinez v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t&rdquo; c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi gi\u1eefa t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00f9ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1097","checkdouble":"190842"},{"date":"11:18 10/07","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong \u0111\u1eddi, Titi mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00e1p l\u1ee5i b\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/goc-nhin-lan-dau-tien-trong-doi-titi-muon-phap-lui-bai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi c\u00e1i t\u00ean Thierry Henry. \u201cTh\u1ea7n gi\u00f3\u201d l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, nh\u01b0ng ri\u00eang \u0111\u00eam nay, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, anh mu\u1ed1n m\u00e0u lam m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThierry Henry t\u1eebng c\u00f3 123 l\u1ea7n h\u00e1t qu\u1ed1c ca Ph\u00e1p trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Les Bleus. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o 1h r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai (11/7), c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u00e1t La Marseillaise vang l\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng song mang l\u1ea1i cho Henry m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1c l\u1ea1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHenry ngh\u0129 g\u00ec trong \u0111\u1ea7u khi qu\u1ed1c ca Ph\u00e1p vang l\u00ean t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n St. Petersburg tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018? Li\u1ec7u anh c\u00f3 c\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfng h\u00e1t khi trong m\u00ecnh \u0111ang mang s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 giao ph\u00f3? Anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y sao khi \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u00e1ch b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Didier Deschamps c\u00f3 v\u00e0i m\u00e9t?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Titi mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00e1p l\u1ee5i b\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Titi mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00e1p l\u1ee5i b\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Tran-dau-Phap-vs-Bi-Lan-dau-tien-Titi-muon-Phap-lui-bai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Henry c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1998</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ai bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Henry. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong \u0111\u1eddi, Henry mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Ph\u00e1p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Anh t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a bi\u1ebft bao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 3 n\u00e0y, Henry s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng \u201cvai \u00e1c\u201d. Anh \u0111ang kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2 n\u0103m qua, Henry l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez. Kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ng\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ph\u00e1p hay kh\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Socola qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng thi\u00ean t\u00e0i. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Titi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u201cn\u1ed9i gi\u00e1n\u201d quan tr\u1ecdng cho B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Henry tai DT bi\" title=\"Henry tai DT bi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Henry-tai-DT-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Henry chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch k\u1ebb th\u00f9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c h\u01a1n, Henry \u0111\u00e3 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng B\u1ec9. T\u1eeb Eden Hazard, Dries Mertens, Michy Batshuayi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n. Lukaku l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh. \u1ede \u0110TQG, anh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201cQu\u00e1i th\u00fa\u201d, kh\u00e1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf CLB Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u1edf d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng khai th\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5. Nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Brazil, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Marcelo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, Olivier Giroud b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi Lukaku c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 b\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Henry. \u201cTh\u1eadt l\u1ea1 khi Henry \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Th\u1ef1c l\u00f2ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee9ng trong h\u00e0ng ng\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Henry \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n sai b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7, \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn nh\u1ea7m n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-phap-nghi-sao-khi-chuan-bi-doi-dau-ke-phan-quoc-henry-421-190824.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nguoi-phap-nghi-sao-khi-chuan-bi-doi-dau-ke-phan-quoc-henry.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-phap-nghi-sao-khi-chuan-bi-doi-dau-ke-phan-quoc-henry-421-190824.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ngh\u0129 sao khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u201ck\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n qu\u1ed1c\u201d Henry?</span><br>\r\n<span>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 khi ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 t\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHenry chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Deschamps, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Juventus. H\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng l\u1ea1 g\u00ec nhau. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng l\u1eabn nhau. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Henry v\u00e0 Deschamps t\u1eebng l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p. H\u1ecd ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng thua d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn khi s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng nhau (21 tr\u1eadn, 16 th\u1eafng, 5 h\u00f2a).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHenry v\u00e0 Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1998 v\u00e0 Euro 2000. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mong mu\u1ed1n, c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi Henry c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 k\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang t\u1edbi c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p. \u201cKh\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u00e0o\u201d, HLV Arsene Wenger n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thierry Henry Phap vs Bi\" title=\"Thierry Henry Phap vs Bi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Thierry-Henry-Phap-vs-Bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac gi\u1eb1ng x\u00e9 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Henry</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Trong th\u1eddi gian qua, b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, Henry \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e3i. Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Giroud v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn nh\u1ea7m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cTh\u1ea7n gi\u00f3\u201d kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Les Bleus ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o ng\u00f3 ng\u00e0ng t\u1edbi anh d\u00f9 v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 8 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2010 t\u1ea1i Nam Phi, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd x\u1ea3y ra \u201cn\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn\u201d. H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd do m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Raymond Domenech \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f4ng, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n l\u1edbn b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Henry World Cup 2010\" title=\"Henry World Cup 2010\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Henry-World-Cup-2010.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">World Cup 2010 l\u00e0 \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi Titi v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u201cl\u00e0m lo\u1ea1n\u201d, c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Henry. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00edch danh anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c n\u1ed5i d\u1eady ch\u1ed1ng HLV Domenech. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo \u201cthuy\u1ebft \u00e2m m\u01b0u\u201d cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a c\u1ee7a Titi v\u00ec b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m 2009, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tranh v\u00e9 v\u1edbt t\u1edbi VCK World Cup 2010 v\u1edbi CH Ireland, Henry \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng tay ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o cho William Gallas ghi b\u00e0n. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Henry \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 t\u1edbi VCK t\u1ea1i Nam Phi, nh\u01b0ng anh b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1eefa l\u00fac kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, Henry kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 b\u1ed1 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Guadeloupe (l\u00e3nh th\u1ed5 h\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p) sinh ra u\u1ea5t h\u1eadn v\u00e0 gi\u1eef trong l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn gi\u1edd n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Henry va Lukaku\" title=\"Henry va Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Henry-va-Lukaku.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Henry c\u00f9ng B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi Henry. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p (FFF)\u201d, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch FFF, Noel Le Graet n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Anh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u00edt li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1ea7n 20 n\u0103m qua, Henry ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i Anh. C\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, anh c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch l\u1edbn h\u01a1n v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Anh kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eb9p c\u00f9ng Les Bleus v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1998 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 20. 12 n\u0103m sau, \u201cTh\u1ea7n gi\u00f3\u201d chia tay Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 32 b\u1eb1ng c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2010.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0a Henry g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p, nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb th\u00f9. \u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n Titi?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-co-nguy-co-bo-lo-tran-dau-phap-vs-bi-421-190807.html\">R\u1ed9 tin Mbappe b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thierry-henry-day-romelu-lukaku-tren-san-tap-truoc-tran-phap-vs-bi-465-190806.html\">Thierry Henry \u0111\u1ea9y Romelu Lukaku tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi-465-190803.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhan-dinh-ban-ket-phap-vs-bi-421-190802.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau-421-190775.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u201cn\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn\u201d \u00c2u ch\u00e2u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1096","checkdouble":"190843"},{"date":"11:28 10/07","title":"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/20/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dna.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Singapore, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 bu\u1ed3n m\u00e0 \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</h2><h2>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/HLV-Hoang-Anh-Tuan-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-U19-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n sau khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Indonesia, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t h\u1eb9p v\u1edbi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1edfi \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Indonesia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, trong khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 Singapore c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;H\u00f4m nay c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n k\u00e9m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Qua gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10 t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n khi \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng mang theo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y khi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c CLB \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng nh\u00ec. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hai chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Qatar tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Indonesia \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup 2019.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-22-u19-singapore-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190804.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-22-u19-singapore-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-22-u19-singapore-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190804.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U19 Singapore (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 to\u00e0n thua c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97-372-190790.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97-372-190790.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U19 Singapore (KT): Chia tay gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 trong n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 to\u00e0n thua c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1095","checkdouble":"190845"},{"date":"07:04 10/07","title":"Luis Enrique l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-la-lua-chon-dung-dan-cho-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Michel Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique sau khi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 La Roja kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n. </h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Enrique ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \u0110T TBN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua, Luis Enrique \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u00d4ng \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1edfi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u1ea5p cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLuis Enrique thay th\u1ebf Fernando Hierro, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1m ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, RFEF \u0111\u00e3 sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui do nh\u1eefng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique, t\u00e2n HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique, t\u00e2n HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Luis-Enrique-len-DT-TBN.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2m l\u00fd b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Salgado \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Enrique</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Michel Salgado c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Luis Enrique c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Hierro, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng HLV c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha\u201d, Salgado ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Enrique trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a FIFA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cEnrique \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Barcelona v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0103n 3, l\u00e0 HLV t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 trong th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ai \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng Hierro trong 2 ng\u00e0y, Enrique c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong \u0111\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha-180-190785.html\">Xavi ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-fernando-hierro-roi-ghe-hlv-truong-cua-tbn-421-190705.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Fernando Hierro r\u1eddi gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-phat-bieu-ve-iniesta-421-190625.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng khi Iniesta b\u1ecb TBN h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-466-190435.html\">World Cup 2018: 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1094","checkdouble":"190812"},{"date":"07:25 10/07","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb Real Madrid b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho M.U v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/sao-tre-real-madrid-bao-tin-buon-cho-mu-va-cac-dai-gia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ec9 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. Nh\u01b0ng ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi Edwin van der Sar \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nB\u1ec9 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNgay t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Sau khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111i qu\u00e1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn l\u00e0 World Cup 2014 v\u00e0 Euro 2016, C\u0110V B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng trong n\u0103m 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Edwin Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Edwin Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Edwin-Van-der-Sar-du-doan-Bi-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bi t\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ai ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. H\u1ecd to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3. T\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil 2-1 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai (11/7). H\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 11/7): \u0110\u1ec9nh cao h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u1edf St. Petersburg</span><br />\r\n<span>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o 90 ph\u00fat ho\u1eb7c d\u00e0i h\u01a1n...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Van der Sar tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 Man United, Edwin van der Sar c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o B\u1ec9. Anh c\u00e0ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf b\u00e9. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Van Der Sar\" title=\"thu mon Van Der Sar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/thu-mon-Van-Der-Sar.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3\u201d, Van der Sar n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Omnisport. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 H\u00e0 Lan, kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.\u201d<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Anderlecht l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Champions League b\u1ecb th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ph\u00e1p, Anh, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u00dd, \u0110\u1ee9c. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf World Cup, nh\u01b0 Croatia. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n.\u201d<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi-465-190803.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhan-dinh-ban-ket-phap-vs-bi-421-190802.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau-421-190775.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u201cn\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn\u201d \u00c2u ch\u00e2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-tran-phap-vs-bi-trung-ve-varane-chi-ra-hai-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-doi-thu-421-190773.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, trung v\u1ec7 Varane ch\u1ec9 ra 2 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-bi-tuyen-bo-danh-bai-brazil-thi-so-gi-phap-421-190771.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: \u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil th\u00ec s\u1ee3 g\u00ec Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br />\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1093","checkdouble":"190813"},{"date":"07:44 10/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/7: 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-107-48-gio-nua-ronaldo-se-la-nguoi-cua-juve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Chelsea t\u00ednh \"h\u1edbt tay tr\u00ean\" m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Man City. </strong>Theo t\u1edd Tuttosport, Chelsea \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli. L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n Maurizio Sarri, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Jorginho t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge thay Antonio Conte. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Chelsea tin \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve. </strong>Theo Sky Sports, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Cristiano Ronaldo sang Juventus s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Jorge Mendes v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid, Florentino Perez s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ecdng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 107 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 107 48 gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Ronaldo-toi-Juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Lewandowski \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern. </strong>Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Pini Zahavi c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 anh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t v\u1edbi Ba Lan, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng d\u00e0nh cho Lewy c\u0169ng v\u01a1i b\u1edbt. Anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern ph\u1ee5ng s\u1ef1 t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u00e2n binh Juventus m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Ronaldo n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t. </strong>Emre Can m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. Juve m\u1edbi g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi Real \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u1edd c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Sterling b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. </strong>Raheem Sterling \u0111ang nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch b\u1edfi phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n v\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Eric Dier v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao Man City nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh. Anh tin c\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Sterling l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling\" title=\"Sterling\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/bo-doi-huyen-thoai-mu-bao-ve-sao-man-city-o-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u1ee3i khen c\u00e1ch Sterling \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xavi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i Lopetegui. </strong>Vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u trong d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ri\u00eang v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xavi, anh \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<br>\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <br>\r\n<strong>C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</strong> Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Arsenal sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 m\u1edbi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi West Ham d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1092","checkdouble":"190814"},{"date":"07:53 10/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 11/7): \u0110\u1ec9nh cao h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u1edf St. Petersburg","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o 90 ph\u00fat ho\u1eb7c d\u00e0i h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1ea1i St. Petersburg.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng danh \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng N'Golo Kante, Blaise Matuidi v\u00e0 Paul Pogba gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o b\u1ecb v\u1ee1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. \u1ede hai c\u00e1nh, Les Bleus c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Antoine Griezmann v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1edfi c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n Benjamin Pavard v\u00e0 Lucas Hernandez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng trong c\u00e1ch tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1edd h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n n\u0103ng. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Ph\u00e1p v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n g\u1ed1c Phi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 117) b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 117) b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 1h ng\u00e0y 11/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u00f2n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0i nghi th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong c\u1ee7a Olivier Giroud. C\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: D\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00ec t\u1edbi nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t. Giroud v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n6/9 b\u00e0n h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ghi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 Mbappe. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Giroud l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann vs Mbappe cua Phap\" title=\"Griezmann vs Mbappe cua Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Griezmann-vs-Mbappe-cua-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann v\u00e0 Mbappe t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ec9 b\u1ee9t l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Ph\u00e1p, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. C\u0169ng v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Khi chuy\u1ec3n sang 4-3-3 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Kevin De Bruyne hay Axel Witsel.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 ngo\u00e0i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t c\u00f2n gi\u00fap h\u1ecd chuy\u1ec3n sang t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao. \u1ede ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 socola c\u00f3 Romelu Lukaku kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi lot vao ban ket World Cup\" title=\"Bi lot vao ban ket World Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Thomas-Vermaelen-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-Bi-vs-Phap-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng B\u1ec9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, Lukaku s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, Eden Hazard khi th\u00ec \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh, khi th\u00ec ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 \u201cs\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o\u201d. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Lukaku l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam Hazard 2 b\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi 1 b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Meunier\" title=\"hau ve Meunier\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/hau-ve-Meunier.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Song h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi thi\u1ebfu Meunier l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn ra m\u1ed9t khu v\u1ef1c c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9. Cho t\u1edbi nay, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 5 b\u00e0n thua v\u1edbi 2 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Tunisia \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil, nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd b\u1ecb k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn 1 b\u00e0n thua c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Martinez.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>N\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ngang t\u00e0i ngang s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng. Gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd nh\u01b0ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t kho\u00e9t c\u00e1nh s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante va Messi\" title=\"Kante va Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Barca-muon-mua-Kante-cua-Chelsea,-khac-tinh-cua-Messi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1p l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n B\u1ec9. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Thomas Meunier do nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. C\u00f2n b\u00ean tr\u00e1i, nh\u1eefng Nacer Chadli hay Yannick Carrasco \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 sau v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Griezmann hay Mbappe? R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n! Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft. Song d\u00f9 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Lloris - 2.Pavard, 4.Varane, 5.Umtiti, 21.Hern\u00e1ndez - 14.Matuidi, 13.Kant\u00e9, 6.Pogba - 10.Mbapp\u00e9, 9.Giroud, 7.Griezmann.<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ec9 (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Courtois - 22.Chadli, 2.Alderweireld, 4.Kompany, 5.Vertonghen - 8.Fellaini, 6.Witsel, 19.Dembele - 9.Lukaku, 7.De Bruyne, 10.Hazard.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 3-2<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Phap vs Bi\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Phap-vs-Bi-(4-3-3-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi-465-190803.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhan-dinh-ban-ket-phap-vs-bi-421-190802.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau-421-190775.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u201cn\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn\u201d \u00c2u ch\u00e2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-tran-phap-vs-bi-trung-ve-varane-chi-ra-hai-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-doi-thu-421-190773.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, trung v\u1ec7 Varane ch\u1ec9 ra 2 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-bi-tuyen-bo-danh-bai-brazil-thi-so-gi-phap-421-190771.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: \u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil th\u00ec s\u1ee3 g\u00ec Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1091","checkdouble":"190815"},{"date":"08:13 10/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/van-der-sar-du-doan-bi-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ec9 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. Nh\u01b0ng ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi Edwin van der Sar \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nB\u1ec9 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNgay t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Sau khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111i qu\u00e1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn l\u00e0 World Cup 2014 v\u00e0 Euro 2016, C\u0110V B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng trong n\u0103m 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Edwin Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Edwin Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Edwin-Van-der-Sar-du-doan-Bi-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bi t\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ai ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. H\u1ecd to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3. T\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil 2-1 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai (11/7). H\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (1h ng\u00e0y 11/7): \u0110\u1ec9nh cao h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u1edf St. Petersburg</span><br />\r\n<span>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o 90 ph\u00fat ho\u1eb7c d\u00e0i h\u01a1n...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Van der Sar tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 Man United, Edwin van der Sar c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o B\u1ec9. Anh c\u00e0ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf b\u00e9. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Van Der Sar\" title=\"thu mon Van Der Sar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/thu-mon-Van-Der-Sar.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Van der Sar d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3\u201d, Van der Sar n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Omnisport. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 H\u00e0 Lan, kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.\u201d<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Anderlecht l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Champions League b\u1ecb th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ph\u00e1p, Anh, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u00dd, \u0110\u1ee9c. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf World Cup, nh\u01b0 Croatia. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n.\u201d<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-dt-bi-465-190803.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhan-dinh-ban-ket-phap-vs-bi-421-190802.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau-421-190775.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u201cn\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn\u201d \u00c2u ch\u00e2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-tran-phap-vs-bi-trung-ve-varane-chi-ra-hai-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-doi-thu-421-190773.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, trung v\u1ec7 Varane ch\u1ec9 ra 2 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-bi-tuyen-bo-danh-bai-brazil-thi-so-gi-phap-421-190771.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: \u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil th\u00ec s\u1ee3 g\u00ec Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br />\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1090","checkdouble":"190816"}]}